  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='Debug|AnyCPU'" />

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='CollegeDebug|AnyCPU'" />

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='HOME_DEBUG|AnyCPU'" />

